arity on\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1758,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/12\/22\/plant-tree-reward-charity\/","url_meta":{"origin":18997,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Charity: Every tree a Muslim plants is rewarded as charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 22, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas bin Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo Muslim plants a tree or sows a seed and then a bird, or a human, or an animal eats from it but that it is charity for him.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2320, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":940,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/07\/22\/spend-o-son-of-adam\/","url_meta":{"origin":18997,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqa: Spend in charity, Allah spends on you","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 22, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Allah said: Spend in charity, O son of Adam, and I will spend on you.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5352, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 993 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5199,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/16\/best-sadaqah-tazkiyyah\/","url_meta":{"origin":18997,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqah: Best charity is most difficult to give","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 16, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: A man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, which charity has the greatest reward?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThat you give charity while you are healthy, greedy, fearing poverty, and hoping to be rich. Do not delay\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14334,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/20\/fulfill-trust-sadaqah\/","url_meta":{"origin":18997,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Charity: Fulfilling trusts honestly an act of charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe honest Muslim storekeeper, who carries out his orders completely, giving with a cheerful heart and paying those whom he was ordered to pay, he is one of two who have given charity.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1371, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u06